[media] saa7134: add AverMedia AverTV/505 card support

Add AverMedia AverTV/505 card to saa7134 driver. It is a card bearing
SAA7130HL chip and FQ1216ME/IH-3 tuner.

Working: Composite, TV and IR remote control.
Untested: S-Video.

